-toll-per-ship/articleshow/131361734.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/90-days-of-middle-east-chaos-us-slaps-sanctions-on-iranian-agency-that-charged-2-million-toll-per-ship/articleshow/131361734.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T07:57:40+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131361750,imgsize-106814.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[LeT turns on its Pakistan masters over recognising Israel]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131361851.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/let-turns-on-its-pakistan-masters-over-recognising-israel/articleshow/131361851.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/let-turns-on-its-pakistan-masters-over-recognising-israel/articleshow/131361851.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T08:14:11+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Raj Shekhar Jha</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131361941,imgsize-40498.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Superman to Clark Kent": Clavicular heavily trolled after quitting testosterone as viral transformation shocks viewers]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131360998.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Looksmaxxing influencer Clavicular, whose real name is Braden Peters, faced intense online criticism after appearing noticeably different following his decision to quit testosterone and other substances. The backlash came weeks after a hospitalization linked to a health scare that prompted him to rethink his lifestyle. While critics mocked his reduced physique, many supporters praised his choice to prioritize long-term health and well-being over maintaining an image built around extreme looksmaxxing practices.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/superman-to-clark-kent-clavicular-heavily-trolled-after-quitting-testosterone-as-viral-transformation-shocks-viewers/articleshow/131360998.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/superman-to-clark-kent-clavicular-heavily-trolled-after-quitting-testosterone-as-viral-transformation-shocks-viewers/articleshow/131360998.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T05:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131360998,imgsize-40582.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Charlie makes me emotional": Candace Owens revisits old Charlie Kirk post after reaching new YouTube milestone]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131360986.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens announced that her YouTube channel has surpassed 6 million subscribers, up from 1.35 million when her independent show launched. She credited viewers for the growth, noting that the platform expanded without advertising or outside investors. Owens also reflected on an old Charlie Kirk post celebrating one million followers, saying its resurgence made her emotional. The milestone highlights the growing influence of independent digital media and audience-driven content creation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/charlie-makes-me-emotional-candace-owens-revisits-old-charlie-kirk-post-after-reaching-new-youtube-milestone/articleshow/131360986.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/charlie-makes-me-emotional-candace-owens-revisits-old-charlie-kirk-post-after-reaching-new-youtube-milestone/articleshow/131360986.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T05:31:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131360986,imgsize-34250.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Why did Adin Ross refuse UFC Freedom 250 appearance despite Donald Trump planning historic White House fight night?]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131360943.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Adin Ross said he will not attend UFC Freedom 250 at the White House after hearing rumors that Benjamin Netanyahu could be there. Ross shared the decision during a Kick livestream and said he prefers watching from home with his father. Meanwhile, UFC and White House staff are preparing the historic June 16 event, with Dana White and Donald Trump promising a massive crowd and celebration.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-did-adin-ross-refuse-ufc-freedom-250-appearance-despite-donald-trump-planning-historic-white-house-fight-night/articleshow/131360943.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-did-adin-ross-refuse-ufc-freedom-250-appearance-despite-donald-trump-planning-historic-white-house-fight-night/articleshow/131360943.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T04:25:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131360941,imgsize-808216.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[“This is so stupid”: Candace Owens challenges Blake Neff over Charlie Kirk and Erika Kirk TPUSA successor claims]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131360939.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens and Blake Neff clashed again on X after Neff appeared to mock Owens’ possible presidential ambitions. Owens responded by demanding proof that Charlie Kirk appointed Erika Kirk as his successor at TPUSA. Their argument quickly spread online, with supporters from both sides reacting strongly. The controversy also renewed public debate around Erika Kirk’s growing role within Turning Point USA.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/this-is-so-stupid-candace-owens-challenges-blake-neff-over-charlie-kirk-and-erika-kirk-tpusa-successor-claims/articleshow/131360939.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/this-is-so-stupid-candace-owens-challenges-blake-neff-over-charlie-kirk-and-erika-kirk-tpusa-successor-claims/articleshow/131360939.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T03:57:49+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131360938,imgsize-2125091.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Valorant streamer GrannyGamingz reveals heartbreaking reason behind return to streaming]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131359096.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A grandmother, GrannyGamingz, is streaming Valorant to fund a headstone for her daughter, Brooke. Brooke, who passed away in 2023, had encouraged her grandmother to become a streamer. GrannyGamingz aims to honor her daughter's memory through her streams. She also seeks legal assistance to share her daughter's story. Viewers are showing strong support for her cause.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/valorant-streamer-grannygamingz-reveals-heartbreaking-reason-behind-return-to-streaming/articleshow/131359096.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/valorant-streamer-grannygamingz-reveals-heartbreaking-reason-behind-return-to-streaming/articleshow/131359096.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T03:04:58+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131359095,imgsize-195562.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Arsenal Thobe for Eid? Zohran Mamdani goes viral in bold football-themed outfit at Eid al-Adha celebration]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131358895.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Zohran Mamdani marked Eid al-Adha in the Bronx wearing a custom Arsenal-inspired thobe, blending religious tradition with football identity during a public appearance alongside Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez. The outfit, adapted from Arsenal’s away kit, drew attention online for its symbolic fusion of culture, faith and sport. Mamdani’s message on solidarity and public service framed the celebration as both personal expression and political statement in New York.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/football/top-stories/arsenal-thobe-for-eid-zohran-mamdani-goes-viral-in-bold-football-themed-outfit-at-eid-al-adha-celebration/articleshow/131358895.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/football/top-stories/arsenal-thobe-for-eid-zohran-mamdani-goes-viral-in-bold-football-themed-outfit-at-eid-al-adha-celebration/articleshow/131358895.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T03:06:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Sports Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131359098,imgsize-1534098.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[From Iran deal ultimatum to Ebola preparedness: Key takeaways from Donald Trump’s cabinet meeting]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131358872.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/from-iran-talks-update-to-ebola-preparedness-key-takeaways-from-donald-trumps-cabinet-meeting/articleshow/131358872.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/from-iran-talks-update-to-ebola-preparedness-key-takeaways-from-donald-trumps-cabinet-meeting/articleshow/131358872.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T02:32:16+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131358883,imgsize-903352.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kick streamer DeenTheGreat faces felony charge over yacht party incident]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131358867.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Kick streamer DeenTheGreat was arrested in Miami after a yacht party fight, facing felony attempted robbery charges. A woman alleged he tried to snatch her phone while she recorded him during an argument, with Ring footage reportedly corroborating the claim. The incident occurred during a livestream with boxer Adrien Broner, leading to Deen's disappearance from the stream and subsequent booking.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kick-streamer-deenthegreat-faces-felony-charge-over-yacht-party-incident/articleshow/131358867.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kick-streamer-deenthegreat-faces-felony-charge-over-yacht-party-incident/articleshow/131358867.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T02:13:32+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/e